data.description: SPECTACULAR LOCATION, LOT & HOME!  3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, 3 Car Garage with a Large Fenced Backyard Retreat!  Seconds to The Villages and NO HOA! There is an OVERSIZED PATIO/LANAI with a hot tub and plenty of room for entertaining and/or family fun!  OPEN FLOOR PLAN that is light, bright & cheery! The living room has built-in plant shelves, recessed lighting & windows that bring in the natural sunlight.  The KITCHEN IS SURE TO IMPRESS offering SOFT-CLOSE WOOD CABINETS & DRAWERS, GRANITE Countertops, Beautiful SS APPLIANCES, CUSTOM BACKSPLASH & a WALK-IN PANTRY.  The Private Master Suite features DUAL SINKS, GRANITE Countertops, wood cabinets, a linen closet and a glass enclosed walk-in shower w/ a built-in seat and beautiful tile work.  The LARGE SECONDARY BEDROOMS are on the opposite side of the home with a secondary bath between the bedrooms. THE SECOND BATH also INCLUDES a WALK-IN SHOWER,  BEAUTIFUL TILE WORK, and GRANITE COUNTER-TOPS.  This side of the home can be closed off by a pocket door, which gives your guests or kiddos their own privacy and space! The inside laundry room is complete with a sink and built-in cabinets. ADDED BONUSES OF THIS HOME: Large bedrooms, irrigation system, home WIFI system, MASSIVE THREE CAR GARAGE, FENCED BACKYARD WITH A DOG RUN, LARGE SCREENED LANAI, CLOSE PROXIMITY TO ALL DAY-TO-DAY CONVENIENCES - WHAT A WONDERFUL PLACE TO CALL HOME!!
